Hi friends =F0=9F=91=8B,
Happy Friday and welcome back to our 41st Weekly Dose of Optimism.
We=E2=80=99re feeling pretty pumped up about everything going on in the wor=
ld right now.
Let=E2=80=99s get to it.
Today=E2=80=99s Not Boring is brought to you by=E2=80=A6 Pesto [ https://su=
bstack.com/redirect/e7e3b156-df1d-4a68-9cbf-660a0b59ed2f?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3=
QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ]
